## windows+linux下安装spark

https://blog.csdn.net/qq_28626909/article/details/81632634

包括安装、pycharm中变量配置（pycharm中跑pyspark）



PYTHONUNBUFFERED=1;

SPARK_HOME=E:\spark-2.4.7-bin-hadoop2.7\spark-2.4.7-bin-hadoop2.7;

JAVA_HOME=E:\spark-2.4.7-bin-hadoop2.7\spark-2.4.7-bin-hadoop2.7\jarsD:\Java\jdk1.8.0_05;

PYTHONPATH=E:\spark-2.4.7-bin-hadoop2.7\spark-2.4.7-bin-hadoop2.7\python

配入环境变量

